subject: Basketball
College Athletics
Athletics and Sports
lead_paragraph: Tyler Hansbrough scored 29 points and Danny Green had 19 last night as No. 1 North Carolina easily held off Penn, 106-71, in their first game at the Palestra in 50 years.
